==Checking the token==
* {{tbox|You can use this token to order gnome food to deliver. You can currently order [X] items.}}
* {{tact|end}}

==Activating the token==
* {{Mes|You have made your order, please be patient while the gnome finds you.}}
* {{tcond|If there is no valid location for the gnome to spawn for 60 seconds:}}
** {{mes|Your food order has timed out. Make sure you're somewhere it can be delivered!}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|Otherwise:}}
** {{tact|A [[mounted terrorchick gnome]] appears after a few seconds and approaches the player.}}
** '''Mounted terrorchick gnome''': {{overhead|Delivery for [player name]!!!}}
** {{tcond|After a few seconds, one of the following:}}
*** '''Mounted terrorchick gnome''': {{overhead|Aluft Aloft delivery for [player name]!!!}}
*** '''Mounted terrorchick gnome''': {{overhead|Make Way!{{sic|"Way" should not be capitalised.}} Package for [player name]!!!}}
** {{tcond|If the gnome can't see the player:}}
*** '''Mounted terrorchick gnome''': {{overhead|Hey, [player name], I can't get to you!}}
** {{tcond|Upon reaching the player:}}
*** '''Mounted terrorchick gnome''': {{overhead|Here you go [player name], your food delivery - still warm!}}
*** {{tact|Gnome food is placed into the player's inventory.}}
** {{tact|end}}
